DESCRPITION
___________


Pleased to pronouce that symmentry is FINISHED. The proscess of creating this map tould about a 2 days.

- A base to spawn in for both teams
- 32 spawn points
- Two bases with sniper tower to spawn in.
- An underground sewer heading to the bomb site.
- Sewer also leads to opisate side of map
- Map Supports all weapons.

___________

INSTALLAION 
___________


place "maps" folder in cstrike folder
